'''爱尔兰银行'''（{{lang-ga|Banc na hÉireann}}；{{lang-en|Bank of Ireland}}），是[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]的四大商业银行之一，于1783年[[英國王室|英國王室]]簽發[[皇家特許狀|皇家特許狀]]後，由{{le|愛爾蘭政府|Government of Ireland}}成立<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rte.ie/news/2011/0331/banks-business.html |title=Banks need fresh €24 billion – Central Bank |date=2011-03-31 |work=RTÉ News |accessdate=2011-03-31 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110403015255/http://www.rte.ie/news/2011/0331/banks-business.html |archivedate= 2011-04-03  }}</ref>。2009年2月27日，一所位于都柏林的分行遭到{{le|2009愛爾蘭銀行搶劫案|2009 Bank of Ireland robbery|抢劫}}，劫匪卷走超过760萬[[欧元|欧元]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=7 arrested after Irish bank heist|url=http://www.iht.com/articles/2009/03/01/europe/irish.php|accessdate=2020-01-30|author=|date=2009-03-01|format=|publisher=[[美聯社|美聯社]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090309070813/http://www.iht.com/articles/2009/03/01/europe/irish.php|archive-date=2009-03-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Concerns over bank security after €7m tiger raid">{{cite news|url=http://www.irishexaminer.com/ireland/idojgbcwkf/|title=Concerns over bank security after €7m tiger raid|date=2009-02-28|accessdate=2009-02-28|newspaper={{le|愛爾蘭考核員|Irish Examiner}}|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090304130047/http://www.irishexaminer.com/ireland/idojgbcwkf|archive-date=2009-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>

